# Coding Rules

- Always follow `.editorconfig` rules for indentation, whitespace, line endings, and final newline.

# Feature: Workflow Automation

When the task relates to the "Workflow Automation" feature, prioritize these locations first:
- `docs/*workflow*.md`
- `docs/*automation*.md`
- `docs/*workflow*.cs`
- `docs/*automation*.cs`
- `src/expose-backend/Expose.Automation/`

- Look also inside linked workspace folders, which contain Temporal- or workflow-related material.

Planned workflow engine: Temporal.
Reference material:
- https://github.com/temporalio/sdk-dotnet
- https://github.com/temporalio/samples-dotnet
